                                            java.lang.String currentPageSize,
                                            SCUIMashupMetaData mashupMetaData,

        This method should return the new page size. If the page size is same as the current page size or if null or empty string is returned, no change is done and return value is ignored. In default implementation this method returns null. The method can be overridden to provide any custom logic. inputEl currentPageSize mashupMetaData uiContext
